b'<p><a href=https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1027354/need-an-unordered-list-without-any-bullets>Relatable post</a></p>
<p>Those black dots you are referencing to are called bullets.</p>
<p>They are pretty simple to remove, just add this line to your css:</p>
<pre><code>ul {
    list-style-type: none;
}
</code></pre>'

